 as I could.\", \"from\": 2430, \"to\": 2482, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It did not matter what the time said on the score.\", \"from\": 2483, \"to\": 2533, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 2506, \"to\": 2514}, {\"ngram\": \"the score\", \"from\": 2523, \"to\": 2532}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am already a winner.\", \"from\": 2534, \"to\": 2556, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a winner\", \"from\": 2547, \"to\": 2555}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am not crying because I have come second, I am crying because it's taken so much to get here.\", \"from\": 2558, \"to\": 2654, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's incredibly hard to win it once, then to win it again, and again.\", \"from\": 2655, \"to\": 2724, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am trying to find new ways to win it.\", \"from\": 2726, \"to\": 2766, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"new ways\", \"from\": 2747, \"to\": 2755}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I can race the best in the world and can come joint-second.\", \"from\": 2767, \"to\": 2826, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 2790, \"to\": 2799}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In my heart I have already won and these are happy tears.\", \"from\": 2827, \"to\": 2884, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my heart\", \"from\": 2830, \"to\": 2838}, {\"ngram\": \"happy tears\", \"from\": 2872, \"to\": 2883}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You can not be upset about that.\\\"\", \"from\": 2885, \"to\": 2918, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Adam Peaty just missed out on a historic third consecutive gold medal in the 100m breaststroke.\", \"from\": 2920, \"to\": 3015, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2920, \"end\": 2930, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Adam Peaty\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\",